      • effectControlFlow

        public void effectControlFlow(int effectUsed)
        Manage the flow of the effects after using one, setting the once that are usable or less. Some effects are only usable before or after other specific effects. For the alternative effect weapon, by default, if one effect is used all usable are set to false
        Overrides:

        Parameters:
